president boarded air force one at 524 pm local time 324 am 
est for the nearly 15hour return trip to washington he made a 
brief stop in alaska for refueling just before noon est 
the presidents audience applauded when he pledged to keep the 
42000 us troops on duty as protection against north korea but 
sat quietly when he talked of trade 
i want you to have this direct from me if we are to keep our 
