base bush told reporters that only time will tell as to whether 
tower will win senate confirmation 
i dont have any predictions nor do i plan to except to say i 
havent wavered one iota and i dont intend to bush said 
asked if towers pledge would help his cause bush shrugged his 
shoulders and said i dont know 
