<TEXT>
he works for the jewish agency in a program to revive soviet 
jewish culture moscows new liberalized policies toward minorities 
are allowing him to do from jerusalem what he couldnt do 10 years 
ago in moscow 
but begun believes that israel is not doing enough to revive 
