ladybugs or which north america has 370 remember tne childrens 
chant ladybug ladybug fly away home your house is on fire 
your children will burn this was a plea by english farmers 
concerned for the safety of ladybugs during the annual burning of 
hop fields 
given a chance an adult egglaying ladybug may consume up to 200 
aphids a day one larva may eat between 200 and 300 during its 
development 
